      "duration_string": "51",
      "view_count": 799,
      "like_count": 2,
      "description": "Join us on April 24, 2016 for an aventure that will always be remembered. Whether you decide to race, ride a personal best or just enjoy the day, the Riviera Nayarit Grand Fondo will be an event that you will never forget!  Our Gran Fondo will take you from La Cruz de Huanacaxtle to Sayulita and back. Over the course of three laps and over 165 km, you will be tested with a total of NINE short but challenging climbs - a total elevation gain of over 1800 meters! In addition, an 8 km section along the coastal road to La Cruz will push the peloton to the limit. If you are coming to race this event - be prepared - at this will be a very tough and competitive race. We expect that the many local and international top athletes that will be in attendance will be setting a blistering pace on the climbs, the flats and the coastal rollers. Come see why Bucerias and the Riviera Nayarit region has been growing rapidly in popularity amongst Mexican, American and Canadian cyclists alike.",
